TITLE: Episode 114 - The Power of Christ Compels You with Scott Johnson
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are joined by a modern-day exorcist. Scott Johnson is a minister, a demonologist, and an exorcist. Join us as we delve into his past, his conversion, his mission, and what it looks and sounds like to go toe-to-toe with demons.
